OL,3,CMan jailed after scamming fans with
OL,4,Cfake Champions League tickets
OL,6,FA man who made made more than #40,000
OL,7,Fselling fake Champions League tickets
OL,8,Fhas been jailed.
OL,10,FLee Waldron, 41, sold the counterfeit
OL,11,FPDF tickets to fans desperate to see
OL,12,FLiverpool FC take on Real Madrid in
OL,13,Fthe 2022 Champions League final in
OL,14,FParis.
OL,16,FBut they were then left devastated
OL,17,Fwhen they discovered their tickets did
OL,18,Fnot work, and were instead fake.
