OL,3,CMan jailed after scamming fans with
OL,4,Cfake Champions League tickets
OL,6,FWaldron, from Kirkby, Merseyside, was
OL,7,Farrested after detectives from the
OL,8,FNorth West Regional Organised Crime
OL,9,FUnit (NWROCU) investigated reports
OL,10,Fmade to Action Fraud by victims who
OL,11,Fhad attempted to buy tickets for the
OL,12,Fbig match.
OL,14,FOfficers then examined bank
OL,15,Ftransactions between the victims and
OL,16,Fsuspects and found that Waldron had
OL,17,Freceived more than #40,000 from
OL,18,Fvictims.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
